data.description: Car enthusiast dream! Meticulously maintained & cared for, this 1-story rambler located just minutes to HWY 410 is a must-see! Entryway leads you to the front bedroom with French doors, & into the open concept kitchen/living/dining. Kitchen boasts gas range, spacious island, & granite countertops. Enjoy the comfort of the fireplace in the winter & AC in the summer! Hard surface flooring. Primary bedroom w/ ensuite & walk-in closet. The outdoor space is spectacular – hot tub, covered patio with knotty pine ceiling, kitchenette, & multiple entertaining spaces! Garden shed, fully fenced, & ready for you! Don’t miss the exterior trim lights, 3-bay garage w/ epoxy floors & a 2-car Triumph car lift!! 8-camera security system stays! Welcome Home!
